[[NewtonWorks]] is an extensible word processor for the Newton. It supports format plugins to enable additional functionality. Among these are Quick Figure Works (which adds spreadsheets), Ebase (which adds simple databases), and Newt Works Draw (which adds drawings). For a How-To on how to hot-rod Newton Works see [[NewtonWorksAddOns]].

[[NewtonWorks]] is [available for free|http://toronto.unna.org/unna/applications/NewtonWorks] at [UNNA](http://www.unna.org).



